    <body>
      <head>Hugo Markt</head>
      <div>
        <p>Pianist who wrote music criticism for the liberal or left-leaning <title level="j">Breslauer Zeitung</title> as well as the social democratic <title level="j">Volkswacht</title>. For years he organized the musical evenings of the Humboldt Society
          in Breslau.</p>

        <p>Markt wrote to Schenker in June 1918 (OJ 2/11, p. 901), but no correspondence between the
          two men is known to survive</p>

      </div>
